<div id="main">
  <div class="top-background"></div>
  <div class="parallax-background"></div>
  <div class="content">

    <div class="top-container">
      <div class="top-insert-outline">
        <div class="top-insert">
          <h1>Velvet</h1>
          <h2 id="velvet-subtitle">By Graham &#38; Spencer</h2>
          <h3>Website Design</h3>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="portfolio-text-insert">
        <h1>Interactive Design</h1>
        <p>Velvet by Graham and Spencer came to DFM looking to move its existing e-commerce business in-house. DFM was asked to design and build a multi-store website for sister brands Velvet and Graham &#38; Spencer. Using the popular Magento e-commerce software, DFM designed both stores as a complement to each existing brand story while adhering to directed design requirements. DFM supports Velvet on a daily basis by acting as its creative department headed up by Velvet's in-house Art Director. </p><br>
        <p id="velvet-page">
          <a href="http://www.velvet-tees.com" target="_blank">http://www.velvet-tees.com</a>
        </p>
        <div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="image-container">
        <%= image_tag "page_velvet/white_outfit.png", :class => "scroll-medium", :id => "white-outfit" %>
        <%= image_tag "page_velvet/three_ladies.png", :class => "scroll-medium", :id => "three-ladies" %>
        <%= image_tag "page_velvet/blue_jacket.png", :class => "scroll-medium", :id => "blue-jacket" %>
        <%= image_tag "page_velvet/computer.png", :class => "scroll-medium", :id => "computer" %>
        <%= image_tag "page_velvet/eight_ladies.png", :class => "scroll-medium", :id => "eight-ladies" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="parallax"></div>

    <div class="bottom-container">
      
      <div id="computers" class="site-page">
        <%= image_tag "page_velvet/computers.png", :class => "scroll-medium" %>
      </div>
      <div class="site-page">
        <%= image_tag "page_velvet/site_page_1.png", :class => "scroll-medium" %>
      </div>
      <div class="site-page">
        <%= image_tag "page_velvet/site_page_2.png", :class => "scroll-medium" %>
      </div>
      <div class="site-page">
        <%= image_tag "page_velvet/site_page_3.png", :class => "scroll-medium" %>
      </div> 
    </div>
    
    <%= partial "layouts/work_with_us" %>
  </div>
</div>